  "text": "Growth refers to the investment opportunity or project that has the potential to grow significantly, bringing profit to the companies [CITATION_1] . New project are often presented to investor and shareholder, as growth opportunities. Since this opportunity can represent a significant fraction of the company value, it would be foolish to forgo them in order to pay out all the earning as dividends to investors and shareholders.",
